  "title": "BEAUTY CENTRE MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>As a Beauty Centre Manager, you will deliver facial, waxing, manicure, pedicure, eyelashes, eyebrow, and laser hair removal treatments while maintaining a clean studio environment and supporting administrative and training activities to ensure excellent client experiences.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct client consultations to assess individual needs and recommend suitable beauty treatments</li><li>Perform facial treatments following established protocols to improve client skin health</li><li>Deliver waxing and laser hair removal treatments safely and effectively to ensure client comfort and safety</li><li>Apply manicure and pedicure services with attention to quality and client satisfaction</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and orderliness of the studio to uphold a hygienic and welcoming environment</li><li>Respond promptly to client enquiries to provide accurate information and support</li><li>Support daily salon operations by completing basic administrative tasks efficiently</li><li>Participate in and lead training sessions to enhance team skills and improve service quality</li><li>Promote and sell beauty products to clients to complement treatments and improve results</li><li>Collaborate with team members to ensure smooth salon operations and high client satisfaction</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum of 10 years of experience in beauty treatments or salon management</li><li>Positive attitude with the ability to create a welcoming and inclusive client environment</li><li>Strong teamwork skills with willingness to learn and take initiative</li><li>Confidence in engaging with clients to enhance their overall experience</li><li>Minimum of Secondary school education or equivalent</li></ul>",
